name: views from the cabin
description: a view of volcán fuego from base camp. as i got to base camp my mind was spinning, i laid down for 20 minutes and then i sat up and this was the immediate view i saw as the sun was on it's way down. i grabbed my camera and knew that this shot would stick with me forever. i conquered this journey, this photo represents to me adventure & courage. shot on 35mm kodak gt 800 film.
